1️⃣ Market Overview
Doddaballapura is rapidly transforming from a textile town into North Bengaluru’s industrial growth corridor. With Foxconn manufacturing momentum, STRR connectivity, and Devanahalli influence, plotted developments are seeing strong mid-segment demand. Investors are entering before full infrastructure maturity — making 2026 a strategic accumulation phase.
